Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Initial Reviewer Selection after the execution of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Average time for SW-Awaiting AE Assignment across all cases in the journal review process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total waiting time to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment following SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Time elapsed from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to the first occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-EIC Reject in rejected manuscript variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants that include SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment compared to the duration of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Cycle time of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs versus variants where it does not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Average time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week'

Name: Total time it takes SW-AE Assign Reviewers after the execution of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in cases leading to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Reviewer Agreed in high-performance variants (performance < median variant duration)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in extended revision cycles
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
